import './Content.css'
import React from "react"
import { Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from '../../views/contents/Inicial'
import Conteudo01 from '../../views/contents/Sobre'
import Conteudo02 from '../../views/contents/Contato'
import Conteudo03 from '../../views/contents/1'
import NaoEncontrado from '../../views/contents/2'

const Content = props => (
    <main className="Content">
        <Switch>
            <Route exact path="/">
                <Home />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/conario">
                <Conteudo01 />
            </Route>
            <Route path="/conteudo02">
                <Conteudo02 />
            </Route>
        </Switch>
    </main>
)
export default Content
